Quote: Give the kids a James Smith spider for their dessert... As a child the spider bar at James Smith in Cuba St was an absolute treat. A James Smith Spider preceded a show at the Opera House or was part of a school holiday on town... Ingredients 1 ball vanilla icecream / 1 300ml bottle Coka-cola [sic] (chilled).
